quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  42,51,"Hazvina kuva zvinopihwa munhu kuti Allah vanotaura naye kunze kwekunge riri shoko rinenge radzikiswa, kana kuti paine chidziro, kana kuti (Allah) vanotumira mutumwa kuti ave anobuditsa zvavanoda nekuda kwemvumo yavo. Zvirokwazvo, ndivo vepamusoro-soro, vazere neungwaru"
  42,52,"Saizvozvo takava tinotumira kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) Rooh (Shoko uye tsitsi) nekuda kwedu. Hawaiziva Gwaro (Qur’aan) kana kuti chii chinonzi kutenda, asi takariita (Qur’aan) sechiedza chatinotungamidza nacho watinoda kubva kuvaranda vedu. Uye zvirokwazvo, (Muhammad (SAW) uri kutungamirira (vanhu) kunzira yakatwasuka (Islaam)"
  42,53,"Nzira yaAllah, avo vari muridzi hwezvose zviri mumatenga nezvose zviri pasi. Zvirokwazvo, zvinhu zvose mukuguma kwazvo zvichadzokera kuna Allah"
  43,1,"Haa – Meem. (Mashoko aya ndemamwe ezvishamiso zviri muQur’aan, uye hapana anoziva zvaanoreva kunze kwaAllah)"
  43,2,Ndinopika neGwaro (Qur’aan) riri pachena (Rinobuditsa zvinhu zvese pachena)
  43,3,"Zvirokwazvo, takariita Qur’aan rive muchirudzi chechiArabhu kuti muve munonzwisisa"
  43,4,"Uye zvirokwazvo (Qur’aan) riri muna Amai veBhuku (Al-Lauh Al-Mahfoodh) nesu, zvirokwazvo ndere pamusoro, rizere neungwaru"
  43,5,"Tochitora here yeuchidzo (Qur’aan) kubva kwamuri, nokuda kwekuti muri vanhu vanopfurikidza mwero"
  43,6,Uyezve vaporofita vangani vatakatumira pakati pevanhu vekare
  43,7,Uyezve hakuna kuuya muporofita kwavari kusara kwekuti vaimuseka
  43,8,"Naizvozvo takaparadza vanhu vakasimba pane ava, uye muenzaniso wevekare wakapfuura (Pamberi pavo)"
  43,9,"Uye zvirokwazvo ukavabvunza: “Ndiani akasika matenga nenyika?” Zvirokwazvo, vachataura kuti: “Samasimba vane ruzivo rwose ndivo vakawasika.”"
  43,10,"Avo vakakugadzirirai nyika semubhedha, uye vakakugadzirirai nzira mairi, kuti muve munotungamirirwa (munofamba zvakanaka)"
  43,11,"Uye avo vanotumira mvura (inonaya) kubva kudenga zvakaenzanirana, naizvozvo tinopa upenyu kuivhu nayo mvura, uye saizvozvo muchava munodzoswa (kuupenyu mushure mekunge mafa)"
  43,12,"Uye avo vakasika zvinhu zvose zviri zviviri zviviri (chirume nechikadzi), uye vakakugadzirirai ngarava nezvipfuyo izvo zvamunotasva"
  43,13,"Kuti muve munotasva kumisana yazvo (zvipfuyo), uye kuti muve munorangarira makomborero aTenzi venyu pamunotasva, uye moti: “Kurumbidzwa ngakuve kune avo vakatungamidza izvi kwatiri, uye hataikwanisa kuzviwana (nekuda kwesimba redu)!”"
  43,14,“Uye zvirokwazvo kuna Tenzi vedu tichadzokera!”
  43,15,"Asi vanovasanganisa (Allah) nechidimbu kubva mune vamwe varanda vavo (vachiti vane vana uye vachivaenzanisa pakunamata). Zvirokwazvo, munhu ari mukusatenda kuri pachena"
  43,16,"Kana kuti (Allah) vakatora vanasikana kubva mune zvavakasika, uye ivo (Allah) vakakusarudzirai imi vanakomana"
  43,17,"Uye kana umwe wavo akaudzwa nezvemashoko (ekuzvarwa kwemwanasikana) zvaanotaura kune Mupi wenyasha (Allah), chiso chake chinosviba uye anozadzwa nekutsamwa"
  43,18,"Uyo anokudzwa achishongedzwa (achipfekedzwa siriki negoridhe, mukadzi), uye asingakwanisi pakupokana kutaura mashoko ari pachena"
  43,19,"Uye vanoita ngirozi izvo dziri varanda veMupi ane nyasha (Allah), vakadzi. Vakamboona kusikwa kwazvo here? Uchapupu hwavo hwuchanyorwa uye vachabvunzwa"
  43,20,"Uye vanoti: “Dai kusiri kuda kweMupi ane nyasha (Allah), tingadai tisina kuzvinamata.” Havana ruzivo nazvo, uye hapana chavanoita kusara kwekunyepa"
  43,21,Kana kuti takavapa rimwe Bhuku mushure meiri (Qur’aan) iro ravarikubatisisa
  43,22,"Asi vanoti: “Takawana madzibaba edu vachitevera imwe nzira nechitendero, uye tinozvitungamirira kuburikidza netsoka dzavo.”"
  43,23,"Uye saizvozvo, hatina kutuma muyambiri mushure mako (Muhammad (SAW)) kune guta ripi zvarwo (vanhu), asi vaigara zvakanaka pakati pavo vakati: “Zvirokwazvo, takawana madzibaba edu vachitevera imwe nzira nechitendero, uye zvirokwazvo ticharamba tichitevera tsoka dzavo.”"